
// This Hyperlambda code sets the value of a [.token] node by concatenating the string "Bearer " with a configuration value retrieved using the [config.get] slot. The [config.get] slot fetches the OpenAI API key from the configuration file using the key path "magic:openai:key". The [strings.concat] slot combines these strings to form a complete authorization token for API requests.
set-value:x:@.token
   strings.concat
      .:"Bearer "
      config.get:"magic:openai:key"
